---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Project Showcase - GigConnect">
  <section class="relative text-center py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-20">
      GigConnect: Event Planning App Concept
    </h1>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-left space-y-12">
      <!-- About GigConnect -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">About GigConnect</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          GigConnect is designed for event organizers, venue managers, and talent coordinators to streamline the process of planning concerts, festivals, and other live events. 
          The platform provides an intuitive way to shortlist artists, manage stage assignments, and schedule performance timesâ€”all from a single interactive interface.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Key Features -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Shortlist artists for events and manage schedules effortlessly.</li>
          <li>Assign artists to stages with available time slots visually.</li>
          <li>Interactive planner with click-to-assign functionality.</li>
          <li>View artist details, tour dates, and contact information in one place.</li>
          <li>Review past bookings with feedback from other event organizers.</li>
          <li>Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile use.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Tech Stack & Tools -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Tech Stack & Tools</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Built with <strong>Astro</strong> for fast static site generation, <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> for responsive and modern UI, and <strong>JavaScript</strong> for dynamic interactivity. 
          Local storage is used to simulate real-time planner functionality.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Future Vision -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Future Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Potential future features include:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Real-time collaboration for multiple organizers.</li>
          <li>Artist profiles with media galleries, social links, and tour history.</li>
          <li>Integration with ticketing platforms and event analytics.</li>
          <li>Notifications and reminders for schedule changes.</li>
          <li>Mobile app support for on-the-go event management.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
